_sText:
Make sure you put the textures in the correct folders or the map won't work correctly. I also noticed that when you download from CSbanana they put an underscore 4 in the name of the zipped folder, if this causes problems let me know I guess. You can also download the map at: 
http://www.freewebs.com/clankfb

Breakmario is just another break map that furthers on the ideas of Tstar's breakfloor and Supa's maps. Its still currently in beta, so new updates can be made soon
